data.description: This residence holds tremendous promise with a bit of tender loving care. An excellent investment prospect! A 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom, 2-car garage dwelling complete with a refrigerator and washer/dryer. Nestled on a cul-de-sac, this home occupies a spacious lot exceeding 1/4 acre in the esteemed Piedmont school district.
